担责任。”特朗普团队的成员说。 目前尚不清楚特朗普是否会采纳上述策略或其他任何一种方案。特朗普“和平方案”曝光：乌克兰20年内不得加入北约 但仍可获美国军援"},"attached_info":"CkEI6oyC3IzmmORnEAMaCTExMTY3OTk1MCDCmLW5BjAAOMwFQA9yCjM1MTYwMDc1MTd4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"42 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-419e1961ae978ca5a4ecd2582a96b85f_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"16_1731061643.56728","card_id":"Q_3426193020","target":{"id":3426193020,"title":"女子漏接市监所电话被辱骂，济南通报，2 人被停职，所长调离岗位，责令向消费者赔礼道歉，如何看待此事？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/3426193020","type":"question","created":1730952937,"answer_count":214,"follower_count":445,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[99,215,307,5582,6546],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"11月6日，济南市市中区市场监督管理局针对“女子反映因漏接电话被市场监督管理所工作人员留言辱骂”一事发布通报。 通报称，经查，网友反映的2人系山东省济南市市中区市场监管局魏家庄市场监管所工作人员。根据相关规定，对2名工作人员予以停职；对魏家庄市场监管所所长调离工作岗位；责令向消费者赔礼道歉。https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/2W5-Dt0hNN_FVH2Vqp-lVg"},"attached_info":"CkEI6oyC3IzmmORnEAMaCTExMTY2MTg2MCDp/bC5BjAAOL0DQBByCjM0MjYxOTMwMjB4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"41 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-c03ff7d29a044938d72b10e2ff21d587_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"17_1731061643.57463","card_id":"Q_3104098505","target":{"id":3104098505,"title":"明朝造船技术已经很发达了，嘉靖年间倭寇犯边，当时朝廷为何不造船训练海军，直插岛国，从根源解决问题呢？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/3104098505","type":"question","created":1730705172,"answer_count":37,"follower_count":79,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[248,144846],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"CkA